ogservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "pod_processes", "rrt", "rrt_max"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["currencyservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-07T15:11:05Z to 2025-06-07T15:33:05Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 15:11:05+00:00 to 2025-06-07 15:33:05+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["currencyservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "pod_processes", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [],\n  \"hypotheses\": []\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "在异常时间范围内（2025-06-07T15:11:05Z至2025-06-07T15:33:05Z），我们收集了链路调用数据，并分析了20个异常调用组合。以下是对这些数据的初步分析，识别出显著的异常调用链：\n\n### 发现的异常\n- **RecommendationService 与 RecommendationService 之间的延迟异常**：\n  - 从 `frontend` 到 `recommendationservice` 的请求，正常平均耗时约为 3855.63ms，而在异常时段耗时显著增加至 64364.44ms，发生频次为44。\n  - 服务名：`recommendationservice` 内部从 `recommendationservice` 到 `ProductCatalogService` 的调用，其正常耗时为2975.9ms，而异常时段耗时增加至42962.86ms，发生频次为44。\n\n- **CartService 的异常**：\n  - 请求路径从 `checkoutservice` 到 `cartservice`，这段调用的正常耗时为2409.52ms，异常时段耗时增加至12075.25ms。\n  - 发生次数为4。\n\n- **ShippingService 的调用异常**：\n  - 从 `frontend` 到 `ShippingService` 的请求有延迟，正常时段耗时为1930.07ms，而异常时段增加到4230.64ms。\n  - 发生次数为3。\n\n### 错误传播路径\n- 延迟主要集中在 `recommendationservice` 以及其与 `productcatalogservice` 的调用之间。\n- 在这期间，`cartservice` 和 `shippingservice` 也出现了耗时增加，这可能是因为它们仍然与较上游的 `recommendationservice` 调用路径相关。\n\n### 错误类型\n- 主要问题似乎是由于系统内某些服务的处理时间过长，而非因网络问题或连接拒绝等错误。\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段耗时增加至64364.44ms，较正常时期的3855.63ms显著延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段耗时增加至42962.86ms，较正常时期的2975.9ms显著延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段耗时增加至12075.25ms，较正常时期的2409.52ms显著延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段耗时增加至4230.64ms，较正常时期的1930.07ms显著延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n尽管这些发现需要进一步的验证和分析，但它们提供了一个关于系统在异常时段内反应情况的初步理解。我们建议进一步分析这些组件以确定具体的根因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析结果，以下是故障期间的异常指标及相关调用链详细信息：\n\n### 异常指标提取\n从 CSV 数据和唯一实体中提取异常指标，特别是变化显著的指标：\n\n- `pod_cpu_usage`: 在所有 `recommendationservice` 服务相关的 Pod (`recommendationservice-0`, `recommendationservice-1`, `recommendationservice-2`)中显著提升。\n- `rrt_max` 和 `rrt`: 推荐服务 (`recommendationservice`) 的响应时间最大值和平均值在 Pod `recommendationservice-0` 和 `recommendationservice-2` 上异常升高。\n- `pod_processes`: Pod `recommendationservice-0`, `recommendationservice-1`, `recommendationservice-2` 的进程数异常增多。\n\n### 异常调用链分析 (假设)\n1. **Recommendationservice Pod**:\n   - **Pod**: `recommendationservice-0`, `recommendationservice-1`, `recommendationservice-2`\n   - **原因**: `pod_cpu_usage` 和 `pod_processes` 指标的显著增加，可能由于内部某个任务或错误导致 CPU 使用暴增和进程异常增长。\n   - **证据**: `pod_cpu_usage` 中值提高到从 0 到 0.4，`pod_processes` 中值从 1 提高到 9。\n\n2. **服务响应时间**:\n   - **Service**: `recommendationservice`\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 指标显著恶化，表明服务响应时间大幅增加，可能导致服务低效或异常。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max` 从 10960 增加到 301001，在服务 `recommendationservice-2`。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"pod_processes\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage and processes count drastically increased.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage median increased from 0.0 to 0.4; pod_processes increased from 1 to 9.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service response time maximum value increased significantly.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 10960 to 301001.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该故障主要集中在 `recommendationservice` 微服务的不同 Pod，可能的问题包括 CPU 使用异常或服务过载。进一步的日志分析和深入故障排查可能有助于确定具体原因。"}
